    <h1>Hello {{ controller_name }}! ✅</h1>

    This friendly message is coming from:
    <ul>
        <li>Your controller at <code>C:/PROJECTS/PersonalProjects/LoanApp/src/Controller/HomeController.php</code></li>
        <li>Your template at <code>C:/PROJECTS/PersonalProjects/LoanApp/templates/home/index.html.twig</code></li>
